'''克里斯蒂安·安東尼·柯隆'''（{{lang-en|Christian Anthony Colón}}，{{bd|1989年|5月14日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的游擊手與二壘手。他先前曾效力過皇家、馬林魚與紅人等隊。
==職業生涯==
===堪薩斯市皇家===
[[2010年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2010年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]，皇家隊在第一輪第4順位選進柯隆。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100607&content_id=10915598&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|title=Royals opt for shortstop Colon with top pick|work=MLB.com|accessdate=November 2, 2015|archive-date=2014-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140815011219/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100607&content_id=10915598&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在2013年11月20日進入40人名單中。<ref name="autogenerated1">{{cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/kc/kansas-city-royals-add-four-to-40-man-roster-drop-three?ymd=20131120&content_id=64080818&vkey=news_kc |title=Royals add four to 40-man roster, drop three |publisher=MLB.com |date=November 20, 2013 |accessdate=December 14, 2013 |archive-date=2014-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140114071848/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/kc/kansas-city-royals-add-four-to-40-man-roster-drop-three?ymd=20131120&content_id=64080818&vkey=news_kc |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2014年， 柯隆在3A的打擊率為2成96。於是他在6月30日升上大聯盟，並在隔日完成初登場。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kansascity.com/sports/mlb/kansas-city-royals/article648069.html|title=Royals bring back Raul Ibanez and call up Christian Colon|work=Kansas City Star|accessdate=November 2, 2015|archive-date=2016-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160810105515/http://www.kansascity.com/sports/mlb/kansas-city-royals/article648069.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>這年皇家隊也闖進了季後賽，而柯隆則在[[2014年美國聯盟外卡晉級賽|外卡賽]]擔任代打。他不但敲出追平安還跑回致勝分。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2014/10/01/352882243/kansas-city-wins-exciting-wild-card-game-over-athletics |title=Baseball's AL Wild-Card Game Was Indeed Wild : The Two-Way |publisher=NPR |date=October 1, 2014 |accessdate=May 17, 2017 |archive-date=2020-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200212195003/https://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2014/10/01/352882243/kansas-city-wins-exciting-wild-card-game-over-athletics |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2015年球季，柯隆沒有固定的守備位置，在球隊擔任工具人。[[2015年世界大賽|2015年世界大賽]]第5場，柯隆在延長賽上場代打，這也是他該年季後賽初登場。而他敲出了致勝安打，幫助皇家拿下睽違30年的世界大賽冠軍。他也成為史上第一位在季後賽首打席就敲出致勝安打的球員。<ref>{{cite web |author=Mike Oz |url=https://sports.yahoo.com/blogs/mlb-big-league-stew/in-his-only-at-bat-of-the-postseason--christian-colon-delivers-the-royals--biggest-hit-090314927.html |title=In his only at-bat of the postseason, Christian Colon delivers the Royals' biggest hit |publisher=Sports.yahoo.com |date=November 2, 2015 |accessdate=May 17, 2017 |archive-date=2017-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170626192651/https://sports.yahoo.com/blogs/mlb-big-league-stew/in-his-only-at-bat-of-the-postseason--christian-colon-delivers-the-royals--biggest-hit-090314927.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2017年開始，Raúl Mondesí主要擔任球隊二壘手。而柯隆也和[[維特·梅利菲爾德|維特·梅利菲爾德]]競爭游擊位置。雖然他進入了球隊開幕戰名單內，<ref>{{cite web |last=Dodd |first=Rustin |url=http://www.kansascity.com/sports/mlb/kansas-city-royals/article142582949.html |title=Caught in roster crunch, Royals' Christian Colon prepared family for 'anything' | The Kansas City Star |publisher=Kansascity.com |date=April 4, 2017 |accessdate=May 17, 2017 |archive-date=2017-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170922053054/http://www.kansascity.com/sports/mlb/kansas-city-royals/article142582949.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過他還是在5月10日遭到球隊指定讓渡。<ref>{{cite web |last=Grathoff |first=Pete |url=http://www.kansascity.com/sports/spt-columns-blogs/for-petes-sake/article149769194.html |title=Royals fans say goodbye to Christian Colon | The Kansas City Star |publisher=Kansascity.com |date=May 10, 2017 |accessdate=May 17, 2017 |archive-date=2018-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181118120735/https://www.kansascity.com/sports/spt-columns-blogs/for-petes-sake/article149769194.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
===邁阿密馬林魚===
5月16日，馬林魚將柯隆從讓渡名單中選走。<ref>{{cite web |last=Dodd |first=Rustin |url=http://www.kansascity.com/sports/mlb/kansas-city-royals/article150814057.html |title=Miami Marlins claim former Royals IF Christian Colon off waivers | The Kansas City Star |publisher=Kansascity.com |date= |accessdate=May 17, 2017 |archive-date=2019-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190829173108/https://www.kansascity.com/sports/mlb/kansas-city-royals/article150814057.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>6月23日，他遭到球隊給指定讓渡。<ref>{{cite web|last=Adams|first=Steve|url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2017/06/marlins-designate-christian-colon-for-assignment.html|title=Marlins Designate Christian Colon For Assignment|publisher=mlbtraderumors.com|date=June 23, 2017|accessdate=June 23, 2017|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028083954/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2017/06/marlins-designate-christian-colon-for-assignment.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>11月6日，他成為自由球員。
===亞特蘭大勇士===
2017年12月6日，他與勇士隊簽下小聯盟合約。不過他在隔年5月9日被球隊釋出。
===紐約大都會===
2018年5月18日，他和大都會隊簽下小聯盟合約。同年11月2日，他成為自由球員。
===辛辛那提紅人===
2018年12月4日，柯隆和紅人隊簽下小聯盟合約。2019年9月16日，紅人買斷他的合約。球季結束後，他再度成為自由球員。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseballamerica.com/stories/minor-league-free-agents-2019/|title=Minor League Free Agents 2019|author=Matt Eddy|website=[[Baseball_America|Baseball America]]|date=November 7, 2019|accessdate=November 8, 2019|archive-date=2019-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191107151148/https://www.baseballamerica.com/stories/minor-league-free-agents-2019/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>不過他在休賽季與球隊續約，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseballamerica.com/stories/minor-league-transactions-nov-3-dec-17-2019/|title=Minor League Transactions: Nov 3 - Dec 17|work=Baseball America|first=Chris|last=Hilburn-Trenkle|date=January 3, 2019|accessdate=January 3, 2019|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129114433/https://www.baseballamerica.com/stories/minor-league-transactions-nov-3-dec-17-2019/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2020年7月24日，他進入了球隊的40人名單內。8月14日，他被球隊放進指定讓渡名單內，而他在三天後被下放到小聯盟。
===堪薩斯市君王===
2021年2月10日，柯隆和美國獨立聯盟的堪薩斯市君王隊簽約。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.americanassociationbaseball.com/transactions/2021-transactions/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-06-20 |archive-date=2021-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228161327/https://www.americanassociationbaseball.com/transactions/2021-transactions/ }}</ref>
===多倫多藍鳥===
2021年4月24日，柯隆和藍鳥隊簽下小聯盟合約。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.oursportscentral.com/services/releases/blue-jays-sign-colon-herrera-to-minor-league-deals/n-5683944 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-06-20 |archive-date=2021-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210429110104/https://www.oursportscentral.com/services/releases/blue-jays-sign-colon-herrera-to-minor-league-deals/n-5683944 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/04/blue-jays-sign-christian-colon.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-06-20 |archive-date=2021-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210510160929/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/04/blue-jays-sign-christian-colon.html }}</ref>他在球季結束後宣布退休。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/12/christian-colon-retires.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2022-01-04 |archive-date=2021-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211224093050/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/12/christian-colon-retires.html }}</ref>
